Q2    Write a program to greet all the person names stored in a list ‘l’ and which starts with S. 

l = ["Harry", "Soham", "Sachin", "Rahul"] 

## Using WHILE LOOP
i=0
name = l.sort()
while (i < len(l)):
    name = (l[i])
    if name.startswith("S"):
        print(name)
    i = i+1

## Using FOR LOOP
item = l.sort()
for item in l:
    if(item.startswith("S")):
        print(item)

    
