Q10     Write a program to print multiplication table of n using for loops in reversed order.



## Using FOR LOOP
num = int(input("Enter number to print table:"))

for i in range(10,0,-1):
    print(f"{num} X {i} = {num*i}")


## Using WHILE LOOP
num = int(input("Enter number to print table:"))
i = 10
while (i<=10):
    print(num,"x",i,"=",i*num)
    i = i - 1
    if i==0:
        break
